Revision history for Perl module Text::CSV::Slurp

1.0 Fri 21 Sep 2012
    - Use IO::File instead of IO::Handle to resolve
        https://rt.cpan.org/Ticket/Display.html?id=78278
    - Convert to Dist::Zilla for distribution

0.9 Thu 03 Feb 2011
    - Clarify documentation to resolve
        https://rt.cpan.org/Public/Bug/Display.html?id=65398

0.8 Mon 11 Jan 2010
    - Add create method

0.7 Tue 29 Sept 2009
    - Update tests to take regard of non-English error output
    - Correct Test::Most version in prereq detail

0.6 Wed 9 Sept 2009
    - More error checking added:
        - now dies with a intelligible message if:
            - it can't read an input file
            - it can't parse the header row successfully
    - Tests added for the above changes
    - Update documentation with license and respository information

0.5 Tue 9 Dec 2008
    - tidy up documentation

0.4 Mon 8 Dec 2008
    - let's bundle things properly this time

0.3 Mon 8 Dec 2008
    - update Changes file

0.2 Mon 8 Dec 2008
    - return a true value

0.1 Mon 8 Dec 2008
    - first release with incomplete test suite


